The Yoneda embedding as a functor `yoneda : C ‚•§ (C·µí·µñ ‚•§ Type v‚ÇÅ)`,
along with an instance that it is `FullyFaithful`.

Also the Yoneda lemma, `yonedaLemma : (yoneda_pairing C) ‚âÖ (yoneda_evaluation C)`.

## References
