/-- The Coyoneda lemma asserts that the Coyoneda pairing
`(X : C, F : C ‚•§ Type) ‚Ü¶ (coyoneda.obj X ‚ü∂ F)`
is naturally isomorphic to the evaluation `(X, F) ‚Ü¶ F.obj X`.

See <https://stacks.math.columbia.edu/tag/001P>.
-/
